  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user i dont want to see all the messages that i have already read before showing up as `unread` when i recover my account\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: I have read all the messages in all chats and when i recovered same account - unread badge appeared . Same happened to @chadyj . Pretty annoying issue taking into account the app performance \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nChats are not shown unread if i have read them and recovered account after\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nunread count appears when i recover account\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create some chats, read all incoming messages\r\n- Recover same account on another device\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: ...\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
